Priya, please be careful while ordering from third party websites. Paranoid, me.

I don’t know if you have heard, but just the other day a 7 year old girl in the UK fell ill due to a cookie from a kawaii related website. She had to be hospitalized with food poisoning. You can read here http://metro.co.uk/2014/04/05/17-year-old-sold-cookie-from-uk-based-cookie-company-but-girl-7-suffered-logistical-headache-slipped-through-traps-4724271/ You can also find the blog post that the seller wrote about it here http://awordyog1b1oom.blogspot.com.es/2012/03/when-customer-rejects-candy-and-is.html

You just never know what can happen and its usually in our best interest to be “over- cautious”… I am Slovenik and we don’t buy things online just don’t trust that!

Well at least you did a great research and knew who to trust!
